{"title":"哦，故乡（外一首）","authors":["贺茂之"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":11,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，故乡（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺茂之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我追寻着你的来历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诠释着你的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣庄！——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我豁然开朗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣庄很小"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘甜如枣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枣庄很纯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯朴如村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那暮雪中的炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缕缕难忘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"童年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁道游击队的童年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浴血台儿庄的战场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作为一名老军人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我仍记得台儿庄街上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那枣树上的弹孔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如历史老人的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然警戒陆海苍茫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万亩榴园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走遍南方北方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还未曾见到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此天然姣色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是民间传说中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仙子遗落的珍珠万斛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是现实中的山亭乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱贫后溢出的笑波？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许这只是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出于人们美丽的想象。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榴园就是榴园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与山后的煤矿相互依托。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工的脸是黑的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但以榴园的泉水洗面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便如榴开时展露皓齿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其美若何？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在千里外的梦中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹榴花数瓣飘落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拣拾起只觉忒沉重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才知是先烈凝血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作今日满园榴火。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}